snippet.title: Atrium Invasion – Official Cinematic Trailer | E3 2021
snippet.description: Your school has been invaded by extra terrestrial beings and only you can stop them! Fight your way through the invasion waves, amplify your speed, strength and defence by unlocking advanced combat equipment! Compete with your friends with our real-time online leaderboards!
